reviews.text: Nice décor and environment. Very comfy to be in. Offer desert and tea set.
I ordered a birthday cake for my boyfriend, but I had requested to reduce the sweetness, they did it! The taste of the cappuccino cake was perfect! We both loved the cake so much!
The apple tart was carefully crafted n put together w fresh apple slices, must try.  The mustang durian desert cake is also very tasty, n also a must try.
蛋糕味道及賣相很好，外賣及堂食質素都不錯，餐廳環境亦很舒服
